							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1" ruledLines="34" writtenLines="34">
									<p>Uniform layout.</p>
									<p>Catchwords on every verso.</p>
									<p>Initial words given in larger, partly square and partly semi-cursive characters. Headings partly ornamented in pen and ink, in black or gold.</p>
